Note on data license:
The Software code is MIT-licensed. Program metadata served via the API /
MCP server is aggregated from Japanese government primary sources (METI, MAFF,
JFC, prefecture public notices, etc.). Those sources are public-domain
(政府公表資料) but the aggregated database structure and presentation are
covered under 著作権法 12条の2 (database copyright). Commercial bulk export
for training corpora requires written consent from Bookyou株式会社
(info@bookyou.net). See /tos.html for the full terms.
